    "description": "<!-- MOBILE DESCRIPTION -->\n<div style=\"display:none\">\n<div vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n<span property=\"description\">The ToolTreaux flat-file set is constructed of high-quality durable steel with a chrome finish, providing durability and resistance to rust and corrosion. They are diamond coated for extra strength, and each features a different grit size ranging from coarse to fine: 40, 80, 150, 240, 400, and 600 grit.<br><br>Each file features a 2” PVC-dipped rubberized handle that will provide comfort, allowing for precision detail work. The non-slip grip will also help prevent injuries during use. Designed with durability in mind, the 6 different files are each 7” in length and have a 3/16” diameter. They are 3mm thick and are embedded on four sides for added strength.<br><br>Diamond flat files are great tools for a number of projects due to their construction and strength</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- MAIN DESCRIPTION -->\n\n\n\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t/* FONTS AND COLORS */\n\t\tbody {\n\t\t\tfont-family: Arial,sans-serif;\n\t\t\tfont-size: 14px;\n\t\t\tline-height: 1.428571429;\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t\tbackground-color: white;\n\t\t}\n\t\th1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n\t\t\tcolor: black;\n\t\t}\n\t\tp {\n\t\t\twhite-space: pre-line;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.navbar a, .navbar a:active, .navbar a:hover, .navbar a:visited {\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.product-specs {\n\t\t\tbackground-color: #f1f1f1;\n\t\t\tpadding: 1em;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.product-specs td {\n\t\t\tfont-size:12px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-left {\n\t\t\tmin-width:6em;\n\t\t\tfont-weight:bold;\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-right {\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tdiv.footer {\n\t\t\tborder-top: 1px solid #f1f1f1;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.navbar-default {\n\t\t\tbackground-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n\t\t\tbackground-image: linear-gradient(t