nds and fun hand tools and accessories; these toy trucks also feature built in handles so playtime adventures can be taken to go for play dates, appointments or travel</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">LIGHTS AND SOUNDS: Bright lights and fun sounds are built into all the toy trucks for the ultimate playtime experience, making it more fun and realistic come playtime with friends and family, inspiring imagination and creativity</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SCREEN FREE PLAYTIME: Sparking curiosity and developing dexterity and hand eye coordination, little one’s will benefit from creative pretend play while they participate in tactile, screen free playtime</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DURABLE AND SAFE: All truck toys and accompanying accessories are safe for children ages 3 and up with adult supervision; Constructed of durable plastic that is easy to clean by wiping down and letting toys air dry</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS: Dimensions: 15 x 6 x 9 inches; Weight: 2.15lbs; Materials: Plastic; Warning: Choking Hazard, Small Parts; For Ages 3 and Up; Batteries Included</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>Kidplokio Assorted Truck Toys with Action Figures Lights Sounds Playset, Ages 3 and Up (2 Styles)</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">49.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Does your little one love trucks? Well, you’re in the right place! Kidplokio’s truck toy carrier play sets come in three themes: Construction, Dinosaur and Fire Truck. Whether it’s a firefighting mission, a construction site building adventure, or prehistoric playtime as a paleontologist, these awesome truck toys for boys are super fun!\n\nBoasting lights, sounds and theme related action figures and accessories, kids will love creating their own pretend play adventures! All the themed truck toys feature lights and with the push of a few buttons, play sounds for the ultimate pretend play experience. Play pretend encourages creativity and imagination, while the tactile playtime experience helps children develop their fine motor skills and dexterity, while moving the action figures and vehicles around their play area. Hello screen free playtime!\n\nDesigned for at home or on the go play, these construction, dinosaur or fire truck toy play sets come with a convenient top carry handle, so little ones can bring their toys along with them on play dates, sleepovers, road trips, appointments and more. The truck toy carrier is easy to tote and travel with, as the sides snap closed, keeping action figures and accessories safety stowed.\n\nAll of the toys and accessories included with these toy truck play sets are safe for children ages three and up with adult supervision. And, made from durable materials, these toy trucks are designed to withstand all the action. For little guys who love construction or fire trucks, this a must have gift from Kidplokio!\nCollect them all!</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>© 2025</p>\n\t\t</div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t</div> <!-- /container -->\n\t<div style=\"clear:both\">\n\t\t&nbsp;<table></table>\n\t</div>\n\n <br>",
    "short_description": "The ToolTreaux flat-file set is constructed of high-quality durable steel with a chrome finish, providing durability and resistance to rust and corrosion. They are diamond coated for extra strength, and each features a different grit size ranging from coarse to fine: 40, 80, 150, 240, 400, and 600 grit. Each file features a 2” PVC-dipped rubberized handle that will provide comfort, allowing for precision detail work. The non-slip grip will also help prevent injuries during use. Designed with durability in mind, the 6 different files are each 7” in length and have a 3/16” diameter. They are 3mm thick and are embedded on four sides for added strength.",
